OL,4,G1300FSusan Calman's Grand Day Out
OL,5,     GSusan takes in wonders of
OL,6,     GWorcestershire, The Malverns and
OL,7,     GMidlands. From speed records to
OL,8,     Gtime travel, she explores
OL,9,     Ghistory, speed, luxury, canals -
OL,10,     Gand the world's smallest theatre!
OL,11,G1400FSusan Calman's Grand Day Out
OL,12,     GSusan tours the north of England,
OL,13,     Ga land forever linked to Wallace
OL,14,     Gand Gromit, sticking to
OL,15,     GYorkshire, where stunning Dales
OL,16,     Gscenery, friendly faces and
OL,17,     Gsurprising local traditions await.
