OL,4,G1700FSusan Calman's Grand Day Out
OL,5,     GSusan follows Ross Poldark's
OL,6,     Gtrail in Cornwall: dancing in
OL,7,     GHelston, scything near Liskeard,
OL,8,     Gsailing in Falmouth, exploring
OL,9,     Gtin mining and the county's
OL,10,     Gwartime history - plus bagpipes!
OL,11,G1800FSusan Calman's Grand Day Out
OL,12,     GSusan goes on a quest in
OL,13,     GSomerset, hunting for signs of
OL,14,     GKing Arthur, taking in
OL,15,     GGlastonbury Abbey, possibly the
OL,16,     Gsite of his tomb; West Somerset
OL,17,     GRailway; and the home of Clarks
OL,18,     Gshoes.
